paragraph.content:
the regulation of the operation of the Mass Transit Railway under the
                    franchise, including all aspects of safety on the Mass Transit
                    Railway;

matters relating to the incorporation of the MTR Corporation Limited, the
                    allotment of shares of the company and the application of various enactments in
                    relation to the company;

subsection.def:
extension (延長部分)
                means, in relation to the railway, an extension provided for in a scheme authorized
                under the Railways Ordinance (Cap. 519);

Mass Transit Railway Corporation
                    (地下鐵路公司) means the entity of that name
                established by section 3(1) of the repealed Ordinance;

paragraph.content:
constitute an assignment, transfer, devolution, parting with possession,
                dealing with or other disposition of that interest for the purposes of any
                instrument concerning or affecting that interest;

section.def:
contract (合約) includes
            any agreement, bond, guarantee or security made or given orally, in writing, by deed, by
            conduct or otherwise;

paragraph.content:
in relation to a contract or a contract of a class of contracts specified
                    in a Vesting Notice, means the date specified in the Vesting Notice for the
                    purposes of section 52B(1);

in relation to a contract or a contract of a class of contracts specified
                    in a Re-vesting Notice, means the date specified in the Re-vesting Notice for
                    the purposes of section 52C(1);

prohibiting or having the effect of prohibiting the vesting under
                        section 52B, 52D, 52E or 52F(1);
                    or

td.def:
“Corporation
                                    (地鐵公司) means the MTR
                                Corporation Limited;”;

td.p:
in Figure Nos. 1 and 2, by repealing “MASS
                                TRANSIT RAILWAY CORPORATION ORDINANCE (CAP. 270)” and substituting “MASS TRANSIT RAILWAY
                                ORDINANCE (CAP. 556)”;

by repealing “Mass Transit Railway
                                    Corporation” and substituting “MTR Corporation
